      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "NN"                 to   w-scr-str-tip          .
           if        w-exe-ctr-001        =    5
                     move  "NA"           to   w-scr-str-tip          .
           perform   cmp-sng-fld-000      thru cmp-sng-fld-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-lst-670.
       exe-exp-lst-680.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
