      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Esportazione [zcp]                                        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       exe-exp-zcp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file area generica                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "dcp "               to   f-xxx-are              .
           move      "zcp "               to   f-xxx-nam              .
           move      "std_dcp_zcp"        to   f-xxx-npe              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
