      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        f-xxx-sts            not  = "S"
                     go to exe-exp-zcp-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuali forzature se esecuzione batch         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-exe-flg-btc        =    "S"
                     go to exe-exp-zcp-010.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
